
  Petabyte(PB)10^15 [facebook servers]
  Exabyte(EB)10^18 [amount of data transfer over the internet]
  Zettabyte(ZB)10^21 [whole data in the world just a few ZB]
  Yottabyte(YB)10^24 [Huge ,No practical use]

1 Terabyte(TB) == 1024 Gigabyte(GB) [large storage HDD]
1 Gigabyte(GB) == 1024 Megabyte(MB) [Movie,Flash Memory]
1 Megabyte(MB) == 1024 Kilobyte(KB) [Image ,Song]
1 Kilobyte(KB) == 1024 Byte [Text Document]
1 Byte == 8 bit 

